{"tid":1479060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【幫手推】國師陳雲再次出謀獻策，遊行前有重大發現，今次教大家點樣捉鬼，唔信陳雲既今次都入黎睇睇！！","createTime":"2019-08-16T18:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:42:59.000Z","uid":305360,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08acc57681f44a06670d98c3b49535378306e2ce","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">成日話，睇人，要長期睇，唔好睇一時</span></strong></span>，因為好多人會突然扮好人，見風駛陀。常言道：知己知彼，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我留意左大師陳雲一段時間，有以下發現，明眼人睇下岩唔岩。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>被嶺大解雇前</strong>：<br />\n其實非常正常，我成日睇佢既書，文化範疇，<ins>時時有高見</ins>。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被解雇後：<br />\n突然<ins>性格大變</ins>。<ins>運用網絡平台，煽動群眾，用學術功底（民俗學 + 語言學），大量闡述似是而非既「高深」說話，自命成為國師</ins>，而無咩獨立思考能力既人，就唯有靠陳雲思考。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">雨傘時期：<br />\n聯同黃洋達既熱血公民及黃毓民既普羅政治，<ins>用「城邦」名義，製造「港獨」帽子，讓中共有口實污名化運動（當時「熱血時報」內地唔洗翻牆都睇到，但系好搞笑，佢地既口號為：打倒共產黨，唔驚內地人睇到？）</ins>。煽動族群仇恨，令香港越來越分化。仲成日話<ins>想「支爆」</ins>。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反送中時期：<br />\n用城邦論失敗，被指證為鬼後，如今放棄推廣，改用第二招：積極喺臉書發表關於美國、請美國幫忙的言論，讓中共有藉口再次污名化運動。更重要既系，<ins>一向要打倒共產黨，想支爆既佢，現在反而說要幫助習總，仲要帶佢作為「中華兒女」既信徒見習大大（習近平怎會見支持港獨既人？）</ins>。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avrAxvL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FavrAxvL.png&h=e4420015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">維穩策略：<br />\n每次都系<ins>將D主流言論用語言藝術、學術用語重新包裝，令人覺得高深莫測；或者事後孔明、馬後炮，製造神機妙算既形象，神化自己</ins>。但系<ins>喺D必然對確既言論入面，會時不時滲透分裂大家、削弱運動既上綱上線言論，或者各界別既（特別系支持香港民主既）領袖有位比佢上時，就會即刻針對相關人等的部分言論（而非該人長期以來既貢獻），呼召支持者群起批鬥。</ins>這是他多年研究中共得出來的策略。估唔到至今喺香港仍然有效。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">眼前事實：<br />\n不斷煽動本土勇武派，教人勇武，但從來系<ins>冷氣軍師，極少出現任何集會。煽動，但從來不會被拘捕。</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">可能性一：<br />\n無食藥（「哲學有計傾」曾經搵佢上節目，陳雲被追問下，<ins>曾指出網上民眾系愚昧的。更被三位主持人發覺其觀點漏洞百出、自相矛盾</ins>；連潘國靈真人認識陳雲，合作過，都話佢突然胡言亂語，可以成為精神分析學案例。） <br />\n<br />\n可能性二：<br />\n兩次運動，應該收左唔少維穩費，<ins>重要時刻打散社運，配合中共劇本（真系離奇吻合）喺本土維穩</ins>。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n前言（支持獨立、鼓動群眾）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njqamps.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnjqamps.png&h=83198412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後語（話人港獨、打散社運）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqRT3C8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqRT3C8.png&h=0ed95b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲一向叫人勇武，<ins>而家又叫人要識收。仲要叫大家818唔好出黎。連和平集會都唔好出！</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">熱普城水軍，陳雲信徒，歡迎批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（讀者不妨起一起浮面批鬥者底），最好有說服力，唔該。預左會比人話P牌，分化撚。</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係邊個係終極分化撚，一清二楚。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">明眼人，幫忙推一推，知己知彼，比大家認識下共產黨幾十年來既招數都好。<ins>歷史應該讓每個人變得聰明，而尼篇文就係照妖鏡。</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以⋯⋯ 都係果句：818，維園見！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"274d754b8ec19b03c4846c2cfdbb78f228369cd5","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推推，唔好再俾鬼分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d55c11a2a1d0b288d472589d247e1edf935441a","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274d754b8ec19b03c4846c2cfdbb78f228369cd5","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推推，唔好再俾鬼分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c30eb41cd274824503145da22b2d4621fda2c26","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274d754b8ec19b03c4846c2cfdbb78f228369cd5","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推推，唔好再俾鬼分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e108f6058e90e996e9040dc32f8bf8aa14f1ba20","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274d754b8ec19b03c4846c2cfdbb78f228369cd5","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"大家幫手推推，唔好再俾鬼分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4bc05619278a38e9ef3a00acc9d63b7baf5c72","tid":1479060,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T18:12:13.000Z","msg":"見你咁有心幫你推一推"},{"pid":"127a762752dea5b5cabf89b0ddb26263e8af72a4","tid":1479060,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc4bc05619278a38e9ef3a00acc9d63b7baf5c72","tid":1479060,"